{"tid":322633,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"樂瞳宣布出性感寫真","createTime":"2017-07-15T03:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T23:22:24.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9559fecc028ce5f15bdd751db6ac6a5e752d31a5","tid":322633,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170707/photo/bkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001_01b.jpg?20170707164415\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170707%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20170707164415&h=c5258804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂瞳透露將於8月推出寫真。<br />\n<br />\n藝人樂瞳接受電台訪問，透露將於8月推出寫真，不過由於一早已計劃下星期去美國洛杉磯過生日，故趕不及在書展期間推出寫真，要等由美國回港後，就會出發到東南亞進行拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>未必接受影全裸相</strong><br />\n<br />\n樂瞳笑言其實早於幾年前已經想出寫真，不過當時仍是無綫藝人，故不會作性感演出，加上尺度好嚴及怕影響形象，所以要等到「29+1」的年齡留倩影。問到今次寫真的性感尺度有幾大？她笑言：「其實都有啲（性感），不過以健康為主，水着相都應該有。之前出第一隻碟都有露背，所以都OK，最緊要係靚同埋唯美就得。（底線去到邊？）未必接受到全裸。（如果遮吓都OK？）諗吓囉，睇吓去完洛杉磯之後，仲keep唔keep到身形。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>30歲前想拍拖</strong><br />\n<br />\n至於談到現時自由身，稍後會有甚麼計劃？樂瞳表示有跟三、四間唱片公司正在談洽中，希望可以推出寫真那段時間會有新歌推出。另外，問到生日願望是否想快啲有拖拍？樂瞳則搞笑反問記者：「乜我好似好想拍拖咩？不過30歲前的確係想settle down，但係一過咗又覺得結唔結婚冇所謂，自給自足唔需要睇人面色都好有安全感。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170707/photo/bkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001_02b.jpg?20170707164415\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170707%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20170707164415&h=9d3b212c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樂瞳最近已密密操弗Body。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170707/photo/bkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001_03b.jpg?20170707164415\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170707%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20170707164415&h=1c1e440b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n期待吧！<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170707/bkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170707%2Fbkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001.html&d=OlRwPETM0fXoJ3tLhRfY1QdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=916a3ee1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170707/bkn-20170707134150839-0707_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"de624734d35d6f7dbd921b9f413335ff8be95fef","tid":322633,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f374538ca700d0af5356618bd4ba81bf537bf12d","tid":322633,"uid":126320,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁嘔心就咪啦<br />\n黐撚線</blockquote><br />\n話比你聽好多好似吾正,其實好L正。有啲日本女優睇落一般,其實正都不得了.<br />\n佢都ok,照殺.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:讀商科啲人吾明工科感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57550fd426acbe19a91074bb71d7c75944069f14","tid":322633,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"賣廣告比班肥老闆睇板？"},{"pid":"c6fdc06cd3b651a51c164bab47597f91f5a199c3","tid":322633,"uid":17761,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁嘔心就咪啦<br />\n黐撚線</blockquote><br />\n話比你聽好多好似吾正,其實好L正。有啲日本女優睇落一般,其實正都不得了.<br />\n佢都ok,照殺.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:讀商科啲人吾明工科感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吾你老母臭閪咩吾吾吾"},{"pid":"882515f6419b65eed51083729bcdb0ab9e320ca0","tid":322633,"uid":27716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:08:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b